text PewterCity_Gym_Text_ExplainTM39 {
    format("A TM, Technical Machine, contains a technique for POKMON.\p Using a TM teaches the move it contains to a POKMON.\p A TM is good for only one use.\p So, when you use one, pick the POKMON carefully.\p Anyways TM39 contains ROCK TOMB.\p It hurls boulders at the foe and lowers its SPEED.")
}

